mes and portfolios. </li>\n     <li><strong>Demo 2: Interactive Engagement:</strong>  Captivate visitors with sticky information and skills sections, while your projects are showcased in an interactive slide-down format, adding a touch of dynamism to your portfolio (NEW). </li>\n<li><strong>Demo 3: Trendy Individuality:</strong>  Make a bold statement with this pre-built design brimming with trendy, creative flair. Showcase your unique personality and stand out from the crowd (NEW). </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/desc-squareroot.png\" alt=\"Onepage WordPress Resume Theme for vCard, CV, Personal Resume\" /></p>\n <strong>Elementor Page Builder Integration for Effortless Customization. </strong> Squareroot makes it super easy to design your website without any coding knowledge. It works perfectly with Elementor, which lets you simply drag and drop elements to create your pages. \n\n	<p> You have complete control over the look and feel of your website, from the overall layout to the smallest details like fonts and colors. Additionally, you can add cool visual effects and animations to make your website stand out. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Compatibility for Seamless Functionality. </strong> Squareroot works perfectly with WPML, so you can easily create a website in multiple languages to reach a global audience. The theme also uses Bootstrap, a popular design tool that makes your website look great and work smoothly on any device, like phones, tablets, and computers. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Mobile-First Design for Optimal Viewing.</strong>  Your website will look stunning and function flawlessly on all devices, ensuring your content is easily accessible to everyone. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Optimized for Speed, Performance, and SEO. </strong> Squareroot is built for speed and performance, ensuring your website loads lightning-fast with an impressive 91% score on both Performance and Accessibility according to Pagespeed Insights. </p>\n\n\n	<p> Plus, with its adherence to 100% of SEO best practices, Squareroot helps your website climb the search engine rankings, attracting more organic traffic and visibility. Keeps visitors engaged and enhances their overall experience. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Dedicated Customer Support for Peace of Mind. </strong> We prioritize your peace of mind with dedicated customer support. You can count on a response to your inquiries within 24 hours, ensuring prompt assistance whenever you need it. During business hours, we prioritize your requests to provide even faster solutions, helping you get back to what matters most. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Detailed customization options for tailored designs. </strong> Squareroot offers detailed customization options, allowing you to tailor your website design to your exact preferences. Every block in the theme is easily editable, giving you complete control over layout, colors, fonts, other visual elements, and more. Allows you to create a unique and personalized online presence that truly reflects your style and brand. </p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Craft your dream online presence and leave a lasting impression with Squareroot NOW.</strong></p>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__squareroot-key-features\"><strong>Squareroot Key Features:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n     <li> Perfect For CV, vCard, Online Portfolio Websites </li>\n     <li> Clean &#38; Modern Design </li>\n     <li> One Click Demo Import </li>\n     <li> One Page &#38; Multi-page Ready </li>\n     <li> Elementor Page Builder </li>\n     <li> Contact Form 7 </li>\n     <li> Fully Drag &#38; Drop </li>\n     <li> Adjustable Column </li>\n     <li> Theme Options and Page Options </li>\n     <li> 3 Pre-Built Websites, more pre-built websites are being created </li>\n     <li> Versatile Post Formats: Standard, Audio, Gallery, Image, Link, Quote, Video, and more </li>\n     <li> Gutenberg Capabilities </li>\n     <li> Detailed Documentation Included </li>\n     <li> Fully Responsive </li>\n     <li> Translation-ready with WPML </li>\n     <li> Included .po/.mo files for easy translation </li>\n     <li> Bootstrap 5 &#38; FontAwesome Icons </li>\n     <li> LESS CSS to optimize loading times </li>\n     <li> Clean Markup </li>\n     <li> Full SEO &#38; Crawling Ability Support </li>\n     <li> Mouse Tracking Effect </li>\n     <li> Support for All Popular Plugins </li>\n     <li> Widgets Ready </li>\n     <li> Page Loading Animation </li>\n     <li> GSAP Animation </li>\n     <li> 600+ Google Fonts </li>\n     <li> Reliable Support </li>\n     <li> And so much more </li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://help.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-support.png\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 1\" /></a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"https://docs.thimpress.com/squareroot/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-document.png\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 2\" /></a>    </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThimPress/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/face-book.png\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 3\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://twitter.com/thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/twitter.png?v=3\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 4\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+Thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/google.png\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 5\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/user/thimpress\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/follow-Tf.png?v=3\" alt=\"Squareroot - WordPress Resume Theme - 6\" /></a> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<h4 id=\"item-description__changelogs\">CHANGELOGS</h4>\n<p><strong>SQRT Resume 3.0.0 • 2024.25.03</stron