(90,1,'2025-05-07 09:52:43','2025-05-07 09:52:43','<p>Censore philosopho possit licebit faciamus accederem demptis emolumento sententiis habetur praetermissa mediocritate salvum solum praeteritis conati cupiditatum praeclare oroete abducam</p><p>Fallare confusioque callido quo maior utrisque maria media instrumento admirabilia loquemur ultima posui</p>','Question 25','','publish','closed','closed','','question-25','','','2025-05-07 09:52:43','2025-05-07 09:52:43','',0,'http://0.0.0.0:8000/questions/question-25/',0,'lp_question','',0),
